data.text: basically i just have very complicated feelings about the fictionalisation of a still existing monarchy and i wonder at what point can this be considered monarchist propaganda?

also very interested to see how far the show will be allowed to push, like i know it’s a historical drama and isn’t intended to be 100% accurate but i expect a degree of accuracy and there are obvs things we don’t know about the royal family which i’m guessing won’t be discussed
